ponse. https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/sBPBdN8NjIRSbldwJ44mqwNHbyw=/0x0:597x571/597x571/filters:focal(299x286:300x287)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/25434451/Screenshot_2024_05_05_at_1.06.15_PM.png]\n\nBut Dorsey hadn’t seemingly been a particularly active participant at the company. In March, when The Verge’s Nilay Patel asked Graeber for Decoder about his level of involvement with Bluesky, she said she gets “some feedback occasionally,” but implied he’s otherwise “being Jack Dorsey on a cloud,” as Nilay put it. Months before that interview, Dorsey had closed his Bluesky account.\n\nBluesky did not immediately respond to The Verge’s request for comment.\n\nUpdate May 5th, 2024, 4:37PM ET: Updated with Bluesky’s confirmation of Dorsey’s departure from its board.\n"}],"package":null,"url":"https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/5/24149543/jack-dorsey-gone-bluesky-board","commentsClosed":false,"railComponents":[{"__typename":"EntryRailNewsletter","entryRailNewsletter":{"name":"Verge Deals","slug":"deals"}}],"dek":{"plaintext":"Bluesky is seeking a replacement board member in the wake of Dorsey’s departure."},"leadImage":{"defaultImageUrl":"https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/KAX3ljrQpb0JQBLUV2gE8_WAbws=/0x0:2040x1360/1200x628/filters:focal(1020x680:1021x681)/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/23951502/VRG_Illo_STK172_L_Normand_JackDorsey_Neutral.jpg","asset":{"title":"Jack Dorsey on a purple background","contentType":"image/jpeg"}},"seoDescription":{"plaintext":"Bluesky has confirmed that Jack Dorsey is no longer a Bluesky board member a day after Dorsey indicated on X that he had left."},"socialDescription":{"plaintext":"Bluesky is seeking a replacement that shares its goals."},"socialImage":null,"shouldUseHTMLNoindex":false,"shouldUseHTMLNofollow":false,"password":null,"additionalContributors":null,"_id":23913584,"leadComponent":{"__typename":"EntryLeadImage","standard":{"hideCredit":false,"asset":{"title":"Jack Dorsey on a purple background"},"caption":null